{"tid":880454,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人好懷念中學考試個環境","createTime":"2018-10-28T17:14:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-28T23:37:34.000Z","uid":136553,"like":12,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1d1efaab233d27c31be3da50ac02f0280edf0836","tid":880454,"uid":136553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T17:14:44.000Z","msg":"今日岩岩考完一科mid term<br />\n係講室入面考<br />\n啲凳同戲院果啲差唔多<br />\n又迫又窄<br />\n放個袋都無位放<br />\n全場坐滿曬人考 完全無space隔住每個人<br />\n個格局就咁 個個迫埋隔離坐 <br />\n好大壓迫感 完全集中唔到<br />\n<br />\n考果陣個腦轉得好慢<br />\n比周圍個環境影響曬<br />\n好多題做唔切 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n翻到屋企望返份卷先發現原來自己根本識做 好快諗到點做<br />\n但偏偏就係考果陣諗唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想他他條條放鬆考試都唔得<br />\n真係好懷念以前中學雞考試果陣排排凳 多活動空間果種考試<br />\n可以放鬆咁考 無咩壓力 反而發揮得仲好"},{"pid":"c13145e282f5078107e3ef386991a53851a7b914","tid":880454,"uid":210524,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T17:23:46.000Z","msg":"中學無壓力，唔識做對成績都冇影響<br />\n點同宜家比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc7a9ae1601b53d8248287b24f903b65dc5a9cef","tid":880454,"uid":9435,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T17:29:09.000Z","msg":"個個都係咁考架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54e8847bb661853601a23f704754837831a8f97f","tid":880454,"uid":155732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T17:51:52.000Z","msg":"考完試既心情 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7ce02e1f81886522a7e8fbb405eb10db06953a8","tid":880454,"uid":208159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T18:07:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ec3786796a7e90f125469fcd99c4192f0c55312","tid":880454,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score